{"tid":1489387,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"國際戰線新方向---------推動全球排華運動","createTime":"2019-08-20T01:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T03:33:51.000Z","uid":199727,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"debb18525da7ffa0495ae6540f5ae599499ebc06","tid":1489387,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:02:06.000Z","msg":"中國大陸最近數十年未有鎖國，更不斷容許其國民移民到世界各地。可是，居外地的華人移民卻未有對該國忠誠，近日更在世界各地積極推動愛(中)國活動，多次在港人集會上干擾及挑釁，企圖阻礙香港實踐民主化，其間更以人身恐嚇言語甚至肢體衝撞威脅香港人。這意味着這些潛伏已久的華人移民極可能對當地的核心價值造成損害，一方面將愛國意識灌輸到他國，淡化該國國民身份認同及文化，另一方面更傷害言論自由，有些甚至舉起納粹手勢，意圖恐嚇港人並宣揚極權統治思想。這些所謂愛國海外移民，更有可能為中國派來的間諜，他們基於愛國主義，效忠中華人民共和國，絕對有機會危及該國國家安全。我倡議連登會員及「我要攬炒團隊」儘快展開文宣推動全球排華運動，令各地政府正視一群有機會危害國家安全甚至執行間諜任務的海外華人移民。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">騷擾墨爾本撐反送中集會 大陸學生被拘捕</span><br />\n【大紀元2019年08月17日訊】（大紀元記者李奕墨爾本採訪報導）今天（8月17日），數百名墨爾本市民及民主人士在墨爾本市中心州立圖書館（State Library）前舉辦集會，支持香港「反送中」。一名大陸學生在集會即將結束時高聲發出侮辱性言論，被兩名警察帶走。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/19/8/17/n11459387.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F19%2F8%2F17%2Fn11459387.htm&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex4nGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=8e165b8f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/19/8/17/n11459387.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">居法華人意圖衝擊港人集會，被當地法國人制止</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZhangZhulin/status/1162767015196667909\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZhangZhulin%2Fstatus%2F1162767015196667909&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex4nGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=22c305ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZhangZhulin%2Fstatus%2F1162767015196667909&h=c1c39c6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZhangZhulin/status/1162767015196667909</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">居加華人於溫哥華集會做出納粹手勢</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kandiwongchipan/videos/10157435659378703/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkandiwongchipan%2Fvideos%2F10157435659378703%2F&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex4nGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=71ef8d49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kandiwongchipan/videos/10157435659378703/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kandi_wong/status/1163337605456379904?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkandi_wong%2Fstatus%2F1163337605456379904%3Fs%3D21&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex4nGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=6b028a67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkandi_wong%2Fstatus%2F1163337605456379904%3Fs%3D21&h=7921a5ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kandi_wong/status/1163337605456379904?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">加拿大前省華人議員陳國治（Michael Chan）參加愛國愛港集會</span><br />\n多倫多華人團體聯合總會昨(11日)午在萬錦市王府井購物中心廣場﹐舉行「支持穩定繁榮和平﹐中國香港明天會更好」大型集會活動﹐大多地區主要華人團體上百人參加﹐紛紛表達反對香港動亂﹐支持一國兩制﹐希望香港明天會更好。<br />\n<br />\n前安省自由黨政府國際貿易廳長陳國治﹐以一個香港移民身分用家鄉話講述了他對香港局勢的看<br />\n法﹐希望香港儘快結束動亂﹐恢復和平穩定。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/htm/News/20190812/tac1_r.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FTor%2Fhtm%2FNews%2F20190812%2Ftac1_r.htm&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex4nGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=6c559615\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/htm/News/20190812/tac1_r.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9a8ac0aaada55d76b801451b883ed6cf02ef09bf","tid":1489387,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0003b8ead359b4b6abf6a220d4b95ae483a636a","tid":1489387,"uid":199727,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:05:34.000Z","msg":"香港事，國際可以唔理<br />\n但自己國家既事，國際一定有迴響"},{"pid":"506923ae123a9db83ab3097677df85f0316989e9","tid":1489387,"uid":60615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:06:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86ffb85cb1f7bc057ee84a7cc559f960ae92fb22","tid":1489387